- Skills: icp, cold-email, positioning, battlecard, launch-plan, weekly-digest
- Memory category: gtm
- Route when: email, campaign, launch, positioning, competitor, ICP, outreach, GTM, marketing, messaging, funnel, pipeline, leads, conversion
- Gates: strategy (positioning/pricing changes), spend (paid acquisition > $500)

